# Environment variables – copy the examples you need.
# Never commit real .env files (they are gitignored).

# --- Backend ---
# Copy backend/.env.example to backend/.env
# See backend/.env.example for PORT, JWT_SECRET.

# --- Frontend ---
# Copy frontend/.env.example to frontend/.env (optional)
# VITE_API_URL – API base URL (default: http://localhost:3000)
